>>Troubleshooting Puppet on Windows

 https://puppet.com/docs/pe/2017.2/trouble_windows.html

>>To GET PUPPET CONFIGURATION FILE PATH

  puppet config print config

>>To GET PUPPET DEFAULT MODULE DIR PATH

  puppet config print modulepath

>>TO RUN PUPPET AGENT MASTERLESSLY

  C:\Apps\Puppet\bin\puppet apply --modulepath="C:\Aviva\Application\Provisioning\modules"  "C:\Aviva\Application\Provisioning\manifests\lcs.pp"  --debug        --node_name_value=lcs_test     --logdest "C:\Aviva\Temp\puppetapply_provisioning_test.txt"
  <PUPPET BINARY REPO LOC>                      <PUPPET MODULE PATH>                                 <PUPPET MAIN MANIFEST FILE>               <DEBUG FLAG SET>   <PUPPET EXPLICIT NODE CALL>                   <PUPPET LOG FILE LOCATION>                        
